  dialogueLines:
  - Greatings there traveler
  - You may not know me but i have met you before.
  - For you see with your fancy little radio you manage to rescue me from quite the
    conundrum
  - I had ended upp trapped in that boorish building
  - Some gears might open that god awful place
  - Your past self said something about there being some in that green house over
    there?
  - Now get on with it i say, my past self is stuck somewhere in that dreaded grey
    shack!
